<HEADLINE>
FT  24 DEC 94 / Weekend Money: Gilt issues - best value v tax status
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Your capital gain on a gilt - a UK government bond - is tax free. However,
you pay tax on the interest. Therefore, gilts which deliver a higher
proportion of their total return as capital gain are more tax efficient, and
 -other things being equal - more attractive to higher rate taxpayers.
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
