Athens-based venture capital group partly-owned by Baring Venture Partners.
The fund will be incorporated in Luxembourg as a closed-end investment
company with a life of 10 years. Private investors are providing 51 per cent
of the fund's capital, with the European Bank for Reconstruction and
Development investing Dollars 8.3m.
