FT  23 DEC 94 / Observer: Global insult
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Just in case Warburgs' chief executive Lord Cairns has not yet received his
Christmas card from Morgan Stanley, Observer warns him not to be too upset
at its contents. People entirely unconnected with the merger flop are
getting the same.
