Musician by Rosso Fiorentino. But the enclosure: a blue stress ball with a
picture of a globe and the legend Morgan Stanley etched upon it - together
with the card's message, 'Season's Greetings and best wishes for a
stressfree 1995]' - might be regarded as a bit below the belt.
